Bird nest
Type: Container

This nest fell out of a tree you were cutting down. Its owner won't be able to find it anymore, so you might as well check what's in it.

Bird nest is an openable treasury item. It can be found by completing various activities. They can have the odds of finding them increased with the Find Bird Nests equipment attribute.

Loot Tables

These are the sub-tables for the various materials, coins, and items that can come from these chests.

These treasury items take 4 independent loot rolls when they are opened.
